headline: My 3 Top Stocks to Buy in a Market That's Highly Volatile (Again)
summary: Dominion Energy is the kind of stable utility stock that's great to own during turbulent markets.  Enbridge has a lower risk than ever before with its midstream and natural gas utility businesses.  Vertex Pharmaceuticals boasts a strong cystic fibrosis franchise along with exciting new products and pipeline candidates.
